title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Collection (IDW Series)
description:
Complete collection of all the IDW TMNT comics released so far in Chronological order. Or as chronological as I can figure. (The most trouble came in the form of the Fugitoid, April and Villain Micros, but I think I got it.)

Contains all current main series issues 1-23, all current Micros, and the complete Secret History of the Foot Clan mini-series.
